  "summary": "OpenStack Image Registry and Delivery Service (Glance) Improper Input Validation vulnerability",
  "details": "The Sheepdog backend in OpenStack Image Registry and Delivery Service (Glance) 2013.2 before 2013.2.4 and icehouse before icehouse-rc2 allows remote authenticated users with permission to insert or modify an image to execute arbitrary commands via a crafted location.",
